title: Lay - Linear Algebra and its Applications 4e + Solution Manual
description:
This is the Linear Algebra and its Applications complete pack by David C Lay, no bullshit. 

This torrent includes 3 .pdfs: the textbook, 4th edition, bookmarked in full. The solution manual for the 4th edition as well as the study guide. The study guide included was also released by David C Lay and was the newest study guide at the time of release of the 4th edition
